Package de.interactive_instruments.etf.client

Interface TestRun

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable
    public interface TestRun
extends java.lang.AutoCloseable
    The information about a started test run is updated at regular intervals and the state can be queried using the methods of this interface. Except the other methods, the result() method blocks until the Test Run finishes.
